Portugal’s Bailout Plan is a ‘Balanced’ Program, Gaspar Says

-- B y   A n a b e l a   R e i s
-- 
2011-10-17T20:11:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-17/portugal-s-bailout-plan-is-a-balanced-program-gaspar-says.html
Portugal ’s bailout plan is
“balanced,” including structural reforms that differentiate it
from other programs, Finance Minister Vitor Gaspar said today in
an interview on RTP1 television station.  Portugal followed Ireland and  Greece  in requesting aid from
the European Union and the International Monetary Fund.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
